										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Madrid is exceedingly hip.  We spent a few days there with our friends Pam and Josh before our week in Morocco, and we returned for a few more days on our own.  We stayed near the Malasaña and Chueca neighborhoods, which are full of vintage shops and great restaurants.</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4763.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1573" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4763-768x1024.jpg" alt="IMG_4763" width="640" height="853" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4763-768x1024.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4763-375x500.jpg 375w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4763.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a><span id="more-1575"></span></p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4530.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1566" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4530-768x1024.jpg" alt="IMG_4530" width="640" height="853" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4530-768x1024.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4530-375x500.jpg 375w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4530.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4526.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1564" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4526-768x1024.jpg" alt="IMG_4526" width="640" height="853" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4526-768x1024.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4526-375x500.jpg 375w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4526.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4520.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1563" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4520-768x1024.jpg" alt="IMG_4520" width="640" height="853" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4520-768x1024.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4520-375x500.jpg 375w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4520.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p>A lot of these streets feel just like the Mission or Hayes Valley, but there are some not-so-subtle reminders you are in Spain:</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4528.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1565" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4528-1024x768.jpg" alt="IMG_4528" width="640" height="480" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4528-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4528-500x375.jpg 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4528.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p>Madrid doesn&#8217;t have a lot of famous, picture-worthy landmarks, but the whole city is just really pretty to look at, especially in autumn:</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4761.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1571" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4761-1024x768.jpg" alt="IMG_4761" width="640" height="480" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4761-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4761-500x375.jpg 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4761.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p>We crossed off several of our must-see-before-we-die paintings, including <em>Guernica </em>and Bosch&#8217;s <em>The Garden of Earthly Delights</em>.  Reina Sofia has one of the most impressive collections I&#8217;ve ever seen, and <em>Guernica </em>was totally worth all the years I waited to see it.  I really wanted to walk through this installation and ring all the bells:</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4515.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1562" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4515-1024x768.jpg" alt="IMG_4515" width="640" height="480" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4515-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4515-500x375.jpg 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4515.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p>A few final pictures as we say hasta luego to Madrid:</p>
<div id="attachment_1570" style="width: 650px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4756.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1570" class="size-large wp-image-1570" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4756-1024x768.jpg" alt="This bear trying to eat strawberries from a tree is a symbol of the city.  J'approve, even though strawberries don't grow on trees." width="640" height="480" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4756-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4756-500x375.jpg 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4756.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1570" class="wp-caption-text">This bear trying to eat strawberries from a tree is a symbol of the city. J&#8217;approve. Even though strawberries don&#8217;t grow on trees I admire the bear&#8217;s effort.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1567" style="width: 650px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4741.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1567" class="size-large wp-image-1567" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4741-1024x768.jpg" alt="Toast with tomato and olive oil is my new favorite breakfast." width="640" height="480" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4741-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4741-500x375.jpg 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4741.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1567" class="wp-caption-text">Toast with tomato and olive oil is my new favorite breakfast.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1572" style="width: 650px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4762.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1572" class="size-large wp-image-1572" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4762-1024x768.jpg" alt="This cat was creepy." width="640" height="480" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4762-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4762-500x375.jpg 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_4762.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1572" class="wp-caption-text">This cat was creepy.</p></div>
